Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:10.94,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,你是做什麼惡夢了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.55,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,我去給你拿杯熱牛奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:14.37,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.72,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,才不是  他存在過的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:18.53,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,一直跟我們在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:19.01,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:19.70,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:25.46,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:30.00,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:40.19,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,好冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:44.45,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,主人  您在這啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.76,0:02:49.05,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,您突然衝了出去讓小多拉很擔心  我還以為出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.41,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,吉普莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:52.36,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,在  您有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:55.57,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,吉普莉爾的主人  是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:58.27,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,為什麼您要在此刻問這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:02:59.16,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:03.06,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,是白小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:06.51,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,那跟吉普莉爾戰鬥過的人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:08.44,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,是白小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:12.34,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,對斯蒂芙提出「愛上我」這要求的是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.16,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,據說是白小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:17.70,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,揭穿東部聯合的遊戲內容的是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.94,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,是白小姐和小多拉爺爺的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:24.63,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,我吉普莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:28.60,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,為白小姐那無與倫比的智慧與謀略著迷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.77,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,才自願侍奉於您的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.96,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,侍奉白？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.43,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.94,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,325)\fs18}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.94,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,艾爾基亞的王兼人類種的全權代理人的您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:39.86,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,白小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:46.41,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,就是說除了白還有另一個人存在？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:49.02,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,但是沒有證據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.42,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,不止是城內
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:54.23,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,我還到城鎮周邊大範圍打聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:59.92,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,{\c&H969696&\3c&H262626&\shad0\move(322.5,125.5,322.5,120)\frz9.271}白的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:59.85,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,嗯  參加抗議遊行的人們也說不知道那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:01.71,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,那就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:09.53,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,主人在我們不知情的情況下跟某人進行對戰  被打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.02,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,最終被篡改了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:14.49,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能  這種事到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.26,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,東部聯合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:19.96,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,嗯  若是他們的話很有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.53,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.15,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,來玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.30,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.70,0:04:35.40,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.80,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,以在主人記憶中的偽造人物為賭注
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:39.77,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,與我進行對戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.13,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,偽造…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.35,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,還有一個十分失禮的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.10,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,懇請主人故意輸給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.67,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,那麼  將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.73,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,偽造…人物…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:58.03,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,真的嗎  那真的是偽造的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.80,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,所以才會消失…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.56,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,吶  白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.78,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,都說人能改變自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:15.57,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,真的能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:17.97,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:21.13,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,全都會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:25.86,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,要是想飛  就能長出翅膀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.09,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,我覺得不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:31.84,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,應該改變的不是自己  而是手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:33.59,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.37,0:05:35.67,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,只能去創造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:41.07,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,創造出能讓現在的自己高飛的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:45.04,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,讓白高飛的方法  我們一起想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:46.86,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,慢慢地想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:51.76,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,全都是  偽造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.31,0:05:55.12,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,全都是  謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.87,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,讓這些消失  就能安心…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:10.22,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,空…白…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:13.37,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.54,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,{\pos(252,325)\fs14}空 白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.54,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,{\pos(346.5,325)\fs14}空 白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.54,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,『　　』  『　　』沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:25.68,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,{\pos(273,324)\fs14}空 白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:25.68,Default_broken,,0,0,0,,『　　』  沒有敗北
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.98,0:06:43.88,*Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼  您要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:46.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥  空是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:50.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,肯定  肯定是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:51.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,空…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:53.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,主人  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:53.35,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22}他存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:54.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,他存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,請冷靜點  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,按理說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:59.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,的確…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:03.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,的確是當他不存在才合理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:06.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是那個人他肯定是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:08.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,小多拉  你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:13.93,*Default,,0,0,0,,因為  白他們怎麼可能會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,斯蒂芙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:17.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  他們不可能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:21.52,*Default,,0,0,0,,肯定有什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:23.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,造就了這種情況的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:26.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,你太無理取鬧了  應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆  昨天幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,在為應對遊行奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:36.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,然後  白就在王座那裡玩遊戲…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:38.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,那是前天  19日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:41.24,*Default,,0,0,0,,我換個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.81,*Default,,0,0,0,,你們前天晚上  去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:49.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你問的就是那天晚上對吧  我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:50.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:51.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,我一點也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,想不起來  這就對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,然後就只剩確認了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:01.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.01,0:08:04.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,我在揉斯蒂芙的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我該做出什麼反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:09.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,你沒感到興奮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:12.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,明明被我要求過「愛上我」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:13.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:18.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是說  要求小多拉「愛上我」的並非主人而另有其人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:21.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯  那是哥提出的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:25.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,可是您不是已經肯定空的存在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:29.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,我到底是為了什麼才被揉胸的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:30.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,謝禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.34,0:08:32.61,*Default,,0,0,0,,因為要是沒有斯蒂芙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:34.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,我就察覺不到這點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:36.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,那麼我們就思考一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.50,*Default,,0,0,0,,那個叫空的人曾存在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,現在卻使其消失的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,在大約一天半的時間內
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:49.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,使他從我們所有人的腦子中消失的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,若是使用大規模的魔法  這並非不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是那樣的話肯定會殘留痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:08:59.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,那如果是遊戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:01.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:05.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果在遵從盟約進行的遊戲中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:08.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,有這種設置的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果是以全權代理人身份進行的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(456.5,325)\fs18}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,那遊戲的影響範圍將會是所有人類種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,可那應該對吉普莉爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.93,0:09:20.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  在侍奉主人的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,我會被當成隨從
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,那我應該也在這影響範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,可是  那到底是什麼樣的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.83,0:09:37.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥他說過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,我相信著白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.15,0:09:46.22,*Default,,0,0,0,,白  我們一直是兩人為一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:50.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥不會  丟下白一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:51.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:54.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,白  你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,白  你還在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.13,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:05.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,隨便哪都行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:09.67,*Default,,0,0,0,,來握住我還有感覺的部位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:11.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,讓我不會瘋掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:20.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.32,0:10:23.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,就算過熱燒毀也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:25.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,拼命思考
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:28.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,這種情況  哥託付於我的這種情況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:32.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,用盡我還記得的所有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:38.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥說過  「我們兩人為一人」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,那麼  哥他就在這
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:46.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥說過  「我們總是在遊戲開始之前就確定了勝利」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,「我們因約定綁在了一起」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:58.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥說過  「我們不是少年漫畫的主人公」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:02.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行  再仔細想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:06.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥說過  「我們去獲取最後一個因素吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:11.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,獲取…為此而進行的對決…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.75,0:11:14.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,在與東部聯合的戰鬥中必須準備的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.43,0:11:18.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,道具  智慧  監視人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(309.5,325)\fs18}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.08,*Default,,0,0,0,,森精種？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,325)\fs18}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:22.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,是要獲取森精種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,那麼要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,去挑戰愛爾文·加爾得？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:28.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,克拉米？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:31.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  克拉米不相信哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,不可能接受這種要求…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:44.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,若是…奪取對方存在的…遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:51.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,白  白
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,//--------------------PART.B--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,爭奪對方存在的遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:11:57.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,構成自身存在的32個棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,根據深層心理的優先順序
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:08.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,把最重要的分為一號  按順序分配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:13.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說  哪個棋子代表著構成自身的哪一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.80,0:12:16.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,在被對方奪走  失去它之前都不會明曉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(373,325)\fs18}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:20.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,比如說你身邊那位森精種的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:23.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,還有手  腳  神經和記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:27.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,到最後連本身存在都被奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,變得完全無法認知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.76,0:12:31.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,也就是會消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,你是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.67,0:12:35.95,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  盟約第五條
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:39.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,「被挑戰方擁有遊戲內容的決定權」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:42.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,你若不接受  那麼這場遊戲就不成立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:44.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,菲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:50.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(372.5,325)\fs18}Imanity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:50.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,這個男人已經發出了賭上人類種的棋子的宣言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:52.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,我不能坐視不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:59.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,真是的  我本以為還有一絲能和解的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:01.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,你想和解的話我可以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,只要你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:05.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(299,325)\fs18}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:05.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,把那森精種交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.07,0:13:06.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:08.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.69,0:13:09.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,要賭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,就賭贏的人能對對方提出兩個要求好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:17.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,比如說  遊戲的結果永久固化
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,將對方的存在永遠抹除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.64,*Default,,0,0,0,,或者篡改對方搭擋某些記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,讓其成為自己人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:28.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說  這是賭上雙方的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:31.33,*Default,,0,0,0,,和搭擋的生殺大權的爭奪戰對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:32.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.25,*Default,,0,0,0,,你瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:42.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就讓我這瘋子多提一個很重要的規則吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.70,0:13:45.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:47.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.16,*Default,,0,0,0,,白  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:51.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.67,0:13:54.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,吉普莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,您有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:14:00.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能製作爭奪存在本身的遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:02.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,不能  讓您失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:06.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,若是像具像化詞語接龍那樣的虛擬世界的話倒是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320.5,325)\fs18}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:08.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,那如果是和森精種共同製作呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:12.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,共同製作？跟那幫森林裡的鄉巴佬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:17.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,大戰時被我用一發天擊就連同首都一起抹除掉的垃圾…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:17.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs22}做得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.40,0:14:20.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,我想並非不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.41,0:14:27.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,因為那幫鄉巴佬挺擅長編造複雜的術式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.03,0:14:30.78,*Default,,0,0,0,,那麼說空就是參與那個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:32.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,將自己的存在抹消了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:34.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,若是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:37.57,*Default,,0,0,0,,那現在這情況不就證明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:39.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,他已經敗北而且被抹消了存在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:40.82,*Default,,0,0,0,,你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:44.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果勝了  空就應該在這
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:48.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果…是還沒輸也還沒贏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:51.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,您說對戰仍在進行中？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:55.63,*Default,,0,0,0,,吉普莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:57.89,*Default,,0,0,0,,在這個房間裡搜索魔法的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.24,0:15:01.45,*Default,,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:11.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,白是在這裡醒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥和白的臥室明明不是在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.84,0:15:15.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,就在這房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:18.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:20.41,*Default,,0,0,0,,「不會丟下白一人」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:26.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,的確感應到有魔法在展開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:28.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,可是我找不出正確的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:32.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,那麼就到處找找吧…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:35.68,*Default,,0,0,0,,小多拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:37.72,*Default,,0,0,0,,竟然會在平坦地面上摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得你已經沒必要再塑造更濃厚的人物性了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.71,*Default,,0,0,0,,我…摔倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:47.94,*Default,,0,0,0,,黑白棋的棋子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是森精語中的三啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:52.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會只有棋子掉在這
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:56.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,因為還沒有使用過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:00.58,*Default,,0,0,0,,就算無法認知  也存在於那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:03.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:06.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,就算知道是黑白棋我們現在也只有這三枚棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.93,0:16:09.20,*Default,,0,0,0,,連我方是黑是白都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,這種事  很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.46,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,「我們兩人為一人」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.71,0:16:19.10,*Default,,0,0,0,,這個遊戲白也在參與
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:22.53,*Default,,0,0,0,,讓我提一個很重要的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,各自的搭擋也參與遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,在玩家無法繼續進行遊戲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:30.07,*Default,,0,0,0,,讓搭擋來代打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:34.39,*Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我才會留有記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:37.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,你能看見嗎  棋盤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:39.31,*Default,,0,0,0,,看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:43.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,如果是哥的話  他會怎麼走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.74,0:16:49.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,你這走法想故意輸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:53.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,不  我這麼走就能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:56.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他會怎樣誘導對手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.44,0:17:01.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是你的記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:06.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,難道說你故意讓我奪走你的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:10.26,*Default,,0,0,0,,來證明自己的背後沒有其他種族的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.34,*Default,,0,0,0,,你這答案挺不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:16.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,知道他會怎樣告訴對方自己的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:31.55,*Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來他就無法繼續遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:33.11,*Default,,0,0,0,,是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:36.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是  遊戲還在繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:39.06,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:41.03,*Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼遊戲沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:47.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,那三枚棋子  到底代表著空的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.81,0:17:50.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,知道他會怎樣欺騙對方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:51.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,他會怎樣去獲得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:04.56,*Default,,0,0,0,,你這種想法任何人都無法看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.22,0:18:09.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,除了哥和白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,在剩下的棋子中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,構成哥的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:16.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,三  遊戲獲勝的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:29.17,*Default,,0,0,0,,二  對白絕不動搖的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.04,0:18:32.18,*Default,,0,0,0,,最後  一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:37.76,*Default,,0,0,0,,屬於白的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.97,*Default,,0,0,0,,好了  哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:45.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,快回到我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:15.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:22.91,*Default,,0,0,0,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.32,0:19:26.14,*Default,,0,0,0,,好  隨便揍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,我已經做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:28.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,…不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:33.77,*Default,,0,0,0,,對不起  對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.37,0:19:39.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,要是白…能早點…早點…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:43.62,*Default,,0,0,0,,我竟然會把主人給忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:45.05,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,克拉米  振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:48.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:52.29,*Default,,0,0,0,,克拉米  克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.53,0:19:53.66,*Default,,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.44,0:19:55.70,*Default,,0,0,0,,就按我的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,提出我的要求好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,你可以隨意處置我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:03.32,*Default,,0,0,0,,但是請讓克拉米…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.83,*Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,要求一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:07.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:12.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,將從對方那奪走的記憶固定並返還
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:16.73,*Default,,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:18.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:21.84,*Default,,0,0,0,,就是保留著從對方那奪來的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:24.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,並將被奪走的記憶取回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:30.12,*Default,,0,0,0,,克拉米和主人就能知曉對方的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.44,*Default,,0,0,0,,成為了對方值得信任的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:36.75,*Default,,0,0,0,,這正是主人所追求的最後一個因素
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:38.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,而…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:39.99,*Default,,0,0,0,,要求二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,325)\fs18}Elf
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:41.28,*Default,,0,0,0,,那邊的森精種
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:45.86,*Default,,0,0,0,,菲爾  我要得到篡改你記憶的權力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:46.48,*Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:47.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.23,0:20:49.27,*Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的  菲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.92,*Default,,0,0,0,,這個男人的要求只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:55.01,*Default,,0,0,0,,想讓我們做間諜是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:59.49,*Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是窺視過我想法的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:00.38,*Default,,0,0,0,,間諜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:01.85,*Default,,0,0,0,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:04.65,*Default,,0,0,0,,之後再和你解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.47,*Default,,0,0,0,,在看過你的記憶之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:11.04,*Default,,0,0,0,,我改變想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:12.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,我助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.36,*Default,,0,0,0,,哥  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:21.74,*Default,,0,0,0,,是吧  我允許你表揚我是讓你自豪的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:26.21,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  你是讓白自豪的哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:30.98,*Default,,0,0,0,,你誇得這麼直白哥哥會害羞的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:33.80,*Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:38.79,*Default,,0,0,0,,白  我不用再忍了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.57,0:21:40.37,*Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.32,0:21:44.42,*Default,,0,0,0,,隨時都準備OK
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:46.40,*Default,,0,0,0,,菲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.23,*Default,,0,0,0,,克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:54.51,*Default,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.02,*Default,,0,0,0,,這種事我不想再來第二次了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.34,0:21:59.19,*Default,,0,0,0,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.36,0:22:03.90,*Default,,0,0,0,,這是  在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:09.96,*Default,,0,0,0,,或許  這也是主人真實的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:17.43,*Default,,0,0,0,,太可怕了！
